title: DataCore SANsymphony: Host Groups
agents: datacore_rest
catalog: storage/datacore
license: GPLv2
distribution: andre_eckstein
description:
 This check monitors host groups configured in a DataCore SANsymphony
 storage system. Host groups are logical collections of hosts that share
 access to virtual disks.

 The check displays the host group status and member information.

 This check requires the special agent configurable through
 "DataCore SANsymphony via REST API".

item:
 The name (Alias) of the host group.

discovery:
 One service is created for each host group.
